title: Quant
description: Hi, Im the president of AQTE (Quant Trading Education). We are so excited to be co-hosting the Intro to Quant event with CCN this upcoming Wednesday (2:30 - 5:30). Thanks Sam for shouting out some of the speakers that will be coming to the event. Hope to see you all in the training and education portion that will be hosted by AQTE. If youre interested in more information, you can check out our post on instagram (handle aqte_uiuc) and sign up using this link: https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScmwHkLWxKJOi516oqU0bdz5XybSeG1yYRt1WAJm06PQovTDA/viewform or the link provided by Sam on the events widget, the 2:45 pm event. I hope to see you there!
